{"pages":[{"title":"Categories","date":"2024-12-31T16:00:00.000Z","path":"categories/index.html","text":""},{"title":"关于","date":"2024-12-31T16:00:00.000Z","path":"about/index.html","text":"关于本站这是一个使用 WikiWarm 主题的个人知识库。 WikiWarm 融合了： Wikitten — 简洁的 Wiki 结构，双栏布局，按目录分类 Warmpaper — 温暖的 Claude 风格配色，方格纸背景，优雅排版 关于作者一个热爱技术与写作的人。 联系我 GitHub: github.com&#x2F;yourname Email: your@email.com"},{"title":"Tags","date":"2024-12-31T16:00:00.000Z","path":"tags/index.html","text":""}],"posts":[{"title":"用户研究方法","date":"2025-07-25T02:00:00.000Z","path":"wiki/Design/UX/user-research/","text":"用户研究方法用户研究是 UX 设计的核心环节。 定性研究 用户访谈 可用性测试 日记研究 定量研究 问卷调查 A&#x2F;B 测试 数据分析 研究流程 确定目标 招募用户 执行研究 分析结果 输出报告","tags":[{"name":"design","slug":"design","permalink":"https://iam-vampire.github.io/uinanlucky.github.io/tags/design/"},{"name":"ux","slug":"ux","permalink":"https://iam-vampire.github.io/uinanlucky.github.io/tags/ux/"}],"categories":[{"name":"Design","slug":"Design","permalink":"https://iam-vampire.github.io/uinanlucky.github.io/categories/Design/"},{"name":"UX","slug":"Design/UX","permalink":"https://iam-vampire.github.io/uinanlucky.github.io/categories/Design/UX/"}]},{"title":"UI 设计原则","date":"2025-07-20T02:00:00.000Z","path":"wiki/Design/ui-design/","text":"UI 设计原则用户界面设计的一些基本原则。 一致性界面元素、操作方式、术语保持统一。 反馈用户操作后给予明确的视觉反馈。 简洁去除不必要的元素，让核心功能突出。 色彩 主色：品牌色 辅助色：信息层级 中性色：文本和背景","tags":[{"name":"design","slug":"design","permalink":"https://iam-vampire.github.io/uinanlucky.github.io/tags/design/"},{"name":"ui","slug":"ui","permalink":"https://iam-vampire.github.io/uinanlucky.github.io/tags/ui/"}],"categories":[{"name":"Design","slug":"Design","permalink":"https://iam-vampire.github.io/uinanlucky.github.io/categories/Design/"}]},{"title":"Jenkins 持续集成","date":"2025-07-16T02:00:00.000Z","path":"wiki/Tech/DevOps/CI-CD/jenkins-guide/","text":"Jenkins 持续集成Jenkins 是老牌的 CI&#x2F;CD 工具。 Pipeline 语法123456789101112131415pipeline &#123; agent any stages &#123; stage(&#x27;Build&#x27;) &#123; steps &#123; sh &#x27;npm 