 build -t my-app .docker run -p 3000:3000 my-appdocker-compose up -d","tags":[{"name":"devops","slug":"devops","permalink":"https://iam-vampire.github.io/uinanlucky.github.io/tags/devops/"},{"name":"docker","slug":"docker","permalink":"https://iam-vampire.github.io/uinanlucky.github.io/tags/docker/"}],"categories":[{"name":"Tech","slug":"Tech","permalink":"https://iam-vampire.github.io/uinanlucky.github.io/categories/Tech/"},{"name":"DevOps","slug":"Tech/DevOps","permalink":"https://iam-vampire.github.io/uinanlucky.github.io/categories/Tech/DevOps/"}]},{"title":"Redis 入门指南","date":"2025-07-05T02:00:00.000Z","path":"wiki/Tech/Backend/Database/redis-guide/","text":"Redis 入门指南Redis 是一个开源的内存数据结构存储系统。 数据结构 String — 字符串 Hash — 哈希 List — 列表 Set — 集合 Sorted Set — 有序集合 应用场景缓存、会话管理、消息队列、排行榜等。","tags":[{"name":"database","slug":"database","permalink":"https://iam-vampire.github.io/uinanlucky.github.io/tags/database/"},{"name":"cache","slug":"cache","permalink":"https://iam-vampire.github.io/uinanlucky.github.io/tags/cache/"}],"categories":[{"name":"Tech","slug":"Tech","permalink":"https://iam-vampire.github.io/uinanlucky.github.io/categories/Tech/"},{"name":"Backend","slug":"Tech/Backend","permalink":"https://iam-vampire.github.io/uinanlucky.github.io/categories/Tech/Backend/"},{"name":"Database","slug":"Tech/Backend/Database","permalink":"https://iam-vampire.github.io/uinanlucky.github.io/categories/Tech/Backend/Database/"}]},{"title":"CSS Grid 布局指南","date":"2025-07-02T02:00:00.000Z","path":"wiki/Tech/Frontend/CSS/grid-guide/","text":"CSS Grid 布局指南CSS Grid 是强大的二维布局系统。 基本概念 Grid Container — 网格容器 Grid Item — 网格项目 Grid Line — 网格线 Grid Cell — 网格单元 示例12345.container &#123; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px;&#125;","tags":[{"name":"css","slug":"css","permalink":"https://iam-vampire.github.io/uinanlucky.github.io/tags/css/"},{"name":"layout","slug":"layout","permalink":"https://iam-vampire.github.io/uinanlucky.github.io/tags/layout/"}],"categories":[{"name